    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, featuring individual throttle bodies and a cross-bank exhaust manifold for peak volumetric efficiency. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers short, mechanical throws, paired with a factory M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque vectoring. The suspension retains its factory-spec Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing a dual-mode character between compliant damping and track-ready stiffness. Recent service includes preventative rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators. While showing minor cosmetic patina reflective of its mileage, the mechanical synchronization and compression across all cylinders remain within tight tolerances. A driver-focused machine with a documented service history.",
      "price": 34500.0,
